-- HTC CORP February Sales Fall 40.08% (Table) : 2498 TT
-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 2012-03-06T07:29:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-06/htc-corp-february-sales-fall-40-08-table-2498-tt.html
HTC CORP (2498)  said unconsolidated sales
in February fell 40.08% to NT$18,600,321,000 from NT$31,041,734,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  2/2012           2/2011
Sales           18,600,321       31,041,734  
YOY%             -40.08%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           34,708,722       65,696,667  
YOY%             -47.17% 
=================================================================
 